      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\tDo you pinkreds really think if there's foul play here with the bank,  that those lawyers wouldn't hunt them down?<br/>\n你们粉红色的人真的认为如果银行有不正当行为，那些律师就不会追捕他们吗？\t\t</div>",
